{"tid":1975541,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"中武肺是種緣份 全首Cover","createTime":"2020-04-16T15:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T01:19:32.000Z","uid":185063,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2790b65c0bf28c27f318ba3bfb6b4779b1b7a5a0","tid":1975541,"uid":185063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"絲打好快手啊，有完整Cover啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚正<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1CZ9xQQ9FY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1CZ9xQQ9FY4&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10MemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=5a4736de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1CZ9xQQ9FY4</a><br />\n<br />\n發起改歌原PO: <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1965677/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1965677/page/2</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n翻唱&amp;後製&amp;MV剪輯：Neko Hime - Catherine Cheng -<br />\n發起改詞：維尼不姓林<br />\n小妹我及一眾連登巴絲s<br />\n<br />\n【中武肺是種緣分】<br />\n原曲：不許你注定一人<br />\n<br />\n看 看著你的臉 病在我枕邊<br />\n疫症在全港蔓延<br />\n你 惹病了感染 病在我眼邊<br />\n武肺元兇彷彿給你加冕<br />\n不管PoPo多改變 只顧這日誓言<br />\n一聲不發在你身邊<br />\n<br />\n不許你注定一人 武肺共你去確診<br />\nptu百樣可能 中武肺是種緣份<br />\n沙展都手震 新冠的親吻<br />\n毅進制計不到幾多確診<br />\n只需要惹病家人 與廢物藍絲警棍<br />\n會全部確診 兩老也陪襯<br />\n登報在新聞 三萬變靈魂 不枉此生<br />\n<br />\n怕 武漢又再解市 封關沒意思<br />\n若有日迷失送中方向不變<br />\n不管中央怎解說 這世衛再決絕<br />\n都想跟你賺多幾轉<br />\n<br />\n差館裏滿是死人 武肺實會有你份<br />\n反黑會跟你一齊 重案個肺都變花<br />\n警嫂都奶中 ICU FULL哂<br />\n外面仲叫緊交通警坐低<br />\n只想會有日可能 兩老合葬的身份<br />\n要預你母親 伯友也陪襯<br />\n不需要慌忙 三萬會齊人 不枉此生<br />\n<br />\n從來不相信831冇你 從來警黑一對<br />\n未確診 被確診 落葬的聲音給方向感<br />\n<br />\n北京咪再扮好人 各國共你去確診<br />\nWHO要扮好人 撐雜總是種緣份<br />\n黑警今鋪要 慌張的抖震<br />\n示意你再不必孤單寄生<br />\n只想會有日可能 黑警唔再搞搞震<br />\n去回望這生 警黑冇床訓<br />\n三萬會陸沉 三萬冇下文 不枉此生"},{"pid":"c1110c49beefea8c998d3a1dabca5f8a65140106","tid":1975541,"uid":31698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8dc588a8baaa32538d2f24504cb6b69d4ae2eb2","tid":1975541,"uid":185063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1110c49beefea8c998d3a1dabca5f8a65140106","tid":1975541,"uid":31698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:38:33.000Z","msg":"只需要惹病家人 與廢物藍絲警棍<br />\n會全部確診 兩老也陪襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8469b8e0fc14630ec061ca118ae7d4151bbf3c99","tid":1975541,"uid":98117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:19:32.000Z","msg":"求入嚟支持一下黃色音樂圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同一位挪威朋友寫咗首歌送比咁多位同路人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1969538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1969538</a>"}]}